                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18410510-name-523" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18410510-name-523" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410510-name-523" type="surname" value="BARNES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410510-name-523" type="given" value="ISAAC"></interp>ISAAC BARNES</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Goswell-terrace, Clerkenwell. The prisoner took a lodging with me for about three weeks—he came home on the 26th of March—I had this coat behind the door in the bed-room—I left it safe before I went out in the morning to work, and when I came home it was gone—I asked the prisoner what he had done with it—he said he had got intoxicated, and left it in the Borough—I said if he was a young man of any principle be would give me the direction where he left it, and I would go after it—he put me off from time to time, saying he would get it.</p>
